      • writeNodeDecl

        protected void writeNodeDecl(XMLWriter xw,
                             String nodeID,
                             int max)
                      throws IOException
        Write a node declaration to GINML. This method will not close the tag to let the caller add child elements, especially parameters.
        Parameters:
        xw - an opened XML writer to save the result
        nodeID - the ID of the component to save
        max - the maximal value of this component (should be at least 1)
        Throws:
        IOException - if writing fails
